snippet.title: Pushy & Pully in Blockland (beta) - Gameplay Madrid Games Week
snippet.description:
We brought this demo to the Madrid Games Week (18-21 Oct.). 

You can see the first World of the game here with some new aditions: 
- new monsters
- new level designs
- time up UFO that chases you to hurry up finishing the level
- added tutorial

I hope you like it! 
Check the presskit of the game: 
http://resistancestudio.com/presskit/sheet.php?p=pushy_pully_in_blockland
Contact us: info[at]resistancestudio.com
